title: Garmin GPS 16x, HVS
description: GPS 16x HVS, MFG# 010-00258-63, High sensitivity 12 channel WAAS GPS sensor. NMEA 0183 output with RJ-45 connector. 12VDC input. The GPS 16x sensor features a high-sensitivity receiver, integrated antenna and rugged, waterproof design that makes it useful for a variety of OEM applications. The GPS 16x is a high-sensitivity GPS sensor that replaces the GPS 16. This high-sensitivity, 12-channel receiver continuously tracks satellites and reports your precise position. It also is WAAS-enabled, so it can determine your precise location to within 3 m (9.84 ft) without using an external DGPS beacon receiver. The GPS 16x offers excellent EMI/RFI performance, so you can use it near mobile computing devices and wireless communications equipment without worrying about interference. GPS 16x
